channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Oscar Mayer Wienermobile Crashes Along Chicago Area Highway
item.description: The hot dog-shaped vehicle hit a car Monday morning and its driver lost control and overcorrected, causing it to roll onto its side on I-294.

item.title: DWP error means thousands of people born in these years are owed thousands each
item.description: The Department for Work and Pensions (DWP) has revealed that thousands of Brits are missing out on an average of £7,293 each due to a state pension error - and some could be owed even more

item.title: Sharks ‘high on cocaine’ after drugs are being flushed down the loo
item.description: It could be affecting their behaviour making them more aggressive.

item.title: Dogs could soon be given ASBOS following spate of 'out of control' incidents
item.description: Under new plans proposed to tackle the rise in dog behaviour incidents, officials have suggested people could be stung with £100 to £1,000 fixed penalty notices for breaking the rules

item.title: Psychic who envisioned Trump assassination attempt gives his US election prediction
item.description: 'I wasn't expecting this to happen until at least August this year.'

item.title: Horror moment battery blows up in man's face in lift leaving his body charred
item.description: WARNING - DISTRESSING FOOTAGE: A 28-year-old man can be seen walking into a lift carrying a lithium battery which starts to smoke after the door closes before exploding

item.title: 14 children end up in hospital after trying ‘adult only’ crisps
item.description: The 'R18' crisps are made using an extract from the ultra-spicy ghost pepper.

item.title: Stalker broke into woman's home, climbed into her bed and sent chilling text
item.description: Adam Lewis became fixated on a woman after meeting her once earlier this year. After repeatedly turning up invited outside her house, his next move was something very sinister…

item.title: Woman describes out of body aura she felt in near-death experience after crash
item.description: 'The experience has allowed me to see the beauty of life.'

item.title: Terrifying moment drunk man 'plays' with deadly cobra before being bitten
item.description: The drunken man was reportedly told to keep his distance from the snake, but decided to pull it towards him as it attempted to retreat from his attempts at 'play'
